Title: Bethe Ansatz solution of the open XX spin chain with nondiagonal

boundary termsAuthors: Rafael I. Nepomechie

Comments: 14 pages, LaTeX; amssymb, no figures

SystemsJournal-ref: J.Phys. A34 (2001) 9993-10004

We consider the integrable open XX quantum spin chain with nondiagonalboundary terms. We derive an exact inversion identity, using which we obtainthe eigenvalues of the transfer matrix and the Bethe Ansatz equations. Forgeneric values of the boundary parameters, the Bethe Ansatz solution isformulated in terms of Jacobian elliptic functions.